{"type": "article", "id": 17967, "title": "前后滚动的刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-24T07:20:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122427Gf7F1lze2acMrkpB.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一把前后滚动的刀，它有一个环形刀片。使用时一手握住上面的绿色把手，一手握住菜，就可以快速滚动切割了。相比起使用普通刀把磨损手腕，它更容易上手也更加灵活。清洗时需打开上面的把手，将刀片取出直接清洗。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1518700692/meet-bolo-the-rolling-knife?ref=nav_search\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122426R3yoeQ9O1VCqEHkw.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53313697\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122426E8jF4zumUZkpHYM2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071224275gco1O9v3LnANbVy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98967552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}